&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;MEMX&lt;/strong&gt; is searching for an Internal Audit Associate to join the Legal &amp;amp; Compliance Team and conduct internal audits to evaluate the effectiveness of system controls and operational processes.&lt;/p&gt;
